data.description: Magnificent custom all brick home located in sought after Veterans High School district. This home has it all! Four BR, 3 bath, formal dining, living room with coffered ceilings, a gas fireplace, and spacious breakfast area and kitchen. Cook like a pro-chef on the gas stove and enjoy serving it up on the beautiful granite countertops while entertaining.  The screened in back porch is ideal for watching the kids play in the swimming pool or spacious yard. But, don't worry there is still space for Mom or dad to relax and enjoy a beautiful rock garden with plants, flowers, and outdoor kitchen. Just a short distance to Robins AFB and shopping.  2.625 % assumable VA loan!
